<h1>Daily Plan: Thursday, January 1, 2026 (New Year Holiday & Strategic Review)</h1>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p><strong>Context:</strong> New Year's Day - light working day. Use for strategic review of Dec 26-31 accomplishments and planning Week 1 priorities.</p>

<p><strong>Objectives:</strong> 3 Light Tasks - Review master plan v0.13, assess readiness for Week 1 infrastructure work (A.2 K8s Readiness), validate E.1 Phase 3 completion.</p>

<h2>Priority 1: Master Plan v0.13 Review & Week 1 Strategy</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Understand current master plan state and identify top 3-5 priorities for Jan 2-8 execution.</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Read MasterPlanCoordination.tt v0.13:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Review Priority Matrix (Section 4)</li>
<li>Identify CRITICAL and HIGH importance items</li>
<li>Note: A.2 (K8s Readiness) marked URGENT BLOCKER</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Extract Week 1 Top Priorities:</strong>
<ul>
<li><strong>A.2: K8s Readiness</strong> - CRITICAL, URGENT (1 week effort)</li>
<li><strong>A.3: Credentials Audit</strong> - CRITICAL, Quick Win (1 week)</li>
<li><strong>E.1: AI Chat Phase 3 Validation</strong> - In Progress (verify widget works end-to-end)</li>
<li><strong>B.1/B.2: Bug Fixes</strong> - HIGH priority (Docker Secrets, Authentication)</li>
<li><strong>F.1: Master Plan IDE Integration</strong> - Can run in parallel with infrastructure work</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Document Week 1 Execution Plan:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Jan 2-7: A.2 Readiness (6 days, primary focus)</li>
<li>Jan 2-4: E.1 validation (parallel, 3 days)</li>
<li>Jan 5-7: A.3 Credentials & B.1/B.2 (overlap with A.2)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 1-1.5 hours | <strong>Deliverable:</strong> Clear understanding of Jan 2-7 priorities</p>

<h2>Priority 2: E.1 Phase 3 Completion Validation</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Verify that widget UI/UX fixes (Chat 2) and backend integration (Chat 1) are working correctly end-to-end.</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Test E.1 Widget Functionality:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Access http://localhost:5000 (or your deployment URL)</li>
<li>Hard refresh browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)</li>
<li>Verify "Chat with AI" button visible and accessible</li>
<li>Click button to open chat panel</li>
<li>Test: Send a sample message</li>
<li>Verify: Response appears in chat panel</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Validate Database Recording:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Check: Conversations recorded in database (inspect ai_conversations table)</li>
<li>Check: Messages recorded in database (inspect ai_messages table)</li>
<li>If missing: Report blocker for Jan 2 investigation</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Document Current Status:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Record: What works (widget UI/UX ✅, backend endpoints ✅)</li>
<li>Record: What needs fixing (database recording ❓)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 30-45 minutes | <strong>Deliverable:</strong> Clear status of E.1 Phase 3 for master plan update</p>

<h2>Priority 3: Dec 26-31 Session Archive Cleanup</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Light administrative work - ensure session history is properly archived.</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Verify Session Archive:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Check: 2025-12-31_session_archive.md exists (full archive of Dec 26-31 work)</li>
<li>Check: current_session.md reset and ready for 2026 work</li>
<li>Check: All chats properly documented with timestamps</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><strong>Optional: Personal Notes</strong>
<ul>
<li>Capture lessons learned from Dec 26-31 sprint</li>
<li>Note: 4-agent workflow (Daily Audit → DocumentationSync → Master Plan Updater → Daily Plans Generator) is operational</li>
<li>Note: coding-standards.yaml v1.0-STABLE now single source of truth for all agent rules</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 15-30 minutes | <strong>Deliverable:</strong> Confirmed session history is clean and archived</p>

